source: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_SEQ_00<tab>Moggzia is looking desperately around the surrounding grass.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_SEQ_00<tab>Moggzia semble avoir perdu quelque chose.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_SEQ_01<tab>A sudden gust of wind has taken Moggzia's precious cloud mallows into its greedy currents. Look for the three pieces that were carried off towards the Mother of the Sheave statue.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_SEQ_01<tab>Une soudaine rafale de vent a emporté les précieux mauves-nuages de Moggzia. Récupérez les trois plantes flottantes qui ont été emportées à l'ouest de L'Écume des cieux de Dravania.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_SEQ_02<tab>You have recovered the three tufts of Moggzia's precious cloud mallow. Return them to the worried moogle.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez récupéré les trois mauves-nuages, comme demandé. Rapportez-les à Moggzia.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_SEQ_03<tab>A noticeable weight lifts off of Moggzia's shoulders when you hand over the mallow tufts he holds so near and dear. It would seem he would have gone hungry without his tufts to use for skyfishing.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_SEQ_03<tab>Moggzia a été très soulagé de récupérer ses mauves-nuages, dont les fruits lui servent de flotteur pour pêcher dans la mer de nuages.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the tufts of cloud mallow to Moggzia.
TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_CAREGIVERMOG01836_100_000<tab>Everyone's perked right up thanks to you, kupo!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_CAREGIVERMOG01836_100_000<tab>Je suis heureux de voir que ma tisane fébrifuge fait son effet. Merci encore pour les ingrédients, kuppo<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_LYINGMOGB01836_100_001<tab>I'd probably still be napping if it wasn't for you, kupo!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_LYINGMOGB01836_100_001<tab>Ne vous inquiétez pas pour moi, je vais vite me remettre. Merci pour tout, kuppo<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_LYINGMOGA01836_100_002<tab>Everything is going well over here, kupo!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_LYINGMOGA01836_100_002<tab>Pfiouuu<var 1D /var>! Quel soulagement<var 1D /var>! Tout est bien qui finit bien, kuppo<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_MOGGZIA_000_010<tab>Oh, no... Without my cloud mallows, I can't do anything, kupopo!

TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_MOGGZIA_000_011<tab>My precious cloud mallows were carried off by a sudden gust of wind! The currents carried them off in the direction of the Mother of the Sheave statue. Adventurer, please, recover my three pieces of cloud mallow before I lose my moogle mind, kupo!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_MOGGZIA_000_011<tab>Mes précieux mauves-nuages ont été emportés par une rafale de vent, kuppo<var 1D /var>! Les courants les ont amenés dans la direction de la statue de Mère Cheveu. S'il vous plaît, retrouvez-les pour moi<var 1D /var>! Il y en avait trois en tout, kuppopo.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_MOGGZIA_000_020<tab>I saw my tufts of cloud mallow fly off in the direction of the Mother of the Sheave statue. My pom-pom is shaking... Please, get them back for me!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_MOGGZIA_000_020<tab>J'ai vu mes trois mauves-nuages s'envoler en direction de la statue de Mère Cheveu... Je vous en prie, retrouvez-les pour moi, kuppo<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_MOGGZIA_000_030<tab>I do hope the beasts around the statue haven't gobbled up my tufts... <var 1A 02 /var>My precious tufts<var 1A 01 /var>! <sob>
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_MOGGZIA_000_030<tab>J'espère qu'aucune des bêtes qui grouillent dans la région n'a mangé mes précieux mauves-nuages, kuppo...

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_MOGGZIA_000_031<tab><gasp> You found them! You found them! Kupopo! I don't know what I would have done without my cloud mallows! They're perfect for skyfishing─now I won't go hungry, kupo!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ525_01860_MOGGZIA_000_031<tab>Bravo, bravooo<var 1D /var>! Aujourd'hui, vous faites le bonheur d'un Mog, kuppo<var 1D /var>! Les fruits des mauves-nuages sont très pratiques, ils nous servent de flotteurs quand on pêche dans la mer de nuages. Vous devriez essayer, vous aussi<var 1D /var>!
